summary: This is an email exchange from November 2021 regarding a spreadsheet containing photos for the Ghislaine Maxwell trial. The email is sent from an FBI agent in New York to an unspecified recipient, offering assistance.

persons.name: R. (NY) (FBI)
persons.context: The sender of the email, identified as an FBI agent from New York, who is providing a spreadsheet of photos for the Maxwell trial.

events.title: Email Exchange Regarding Maxwell Trial Photos
events.description: An FBI agent emails a spreadsheet containing photos intended for use in the Ghislaine Maxwell trial.

keyFacts: An FBI agent from New York was involved in preparing photographic evidence for the Ghislaine Maxwell trial as of November 2021.
A spreadsheet containing photos for the Maxwell trial was circulated via email among law enforcement/prosecution personnel.
The document indicates ongoing trial preparation activities by law enforcement close to the trial date.
